<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="link-vt">link <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /lɪŋk/    美 /lɪŋk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-connect">1.★ <strong>连接；联系(connect)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He walked with her, <strong>linking arms</strong>.
他与她挽臂同行。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="link-to-with">link ... to / with</h3>
<p>1.<strong>把…连接 / 联系起来：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A subway line will link the airport to the city centre.
地铁将把机场和市中心连接起来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Yellow is linked with confidence, self-respect and friendliness.  
黄色一般与自信、自尊和友好相关。</p></div></div>